Sub-Task description: "Create all required HTML template files for the 'SmartHomeManager' web application inside the Flask 'templates' directory. Templates to create are  dashboard.html, device_list.html, device_control.html, add_device.html, automation_rules.html, energy_report.html, and activity_logs.html. Each template must include the specified page title and all required elements with the exact IDs as defined in the requirements document. The templates should be structured to receive and display data passed from main.py, including dynamic content such as device lists, automation rules, energy data, and activity logs. Ensure templates support navigation buttons linking to the correct routes."
